John Galkowski, 118 pounds, decisioned his opponent 5-3. Galkowski went ahead 5-1 on a near-fall in the second round, and held on to defeat the Gators’ Rick Goodwin. The win brings his record to 7-3-1. Darren Rodriguez of the Mustangs won the most exciting match of the night, 10-9, in the 126-pound weight class.
